[pintu ditutup]

01:32:56.666 --> 01:32:58.041
[nada tunggu telepon]

01:33:02.458 --> 01:33:03.500
[Barra] Asalamualaikum.

01:33:03.583 --> 01:33:05.208
[Ica] Wa alaikumsalam, Barra.

