Aku sama Amel udah selesai.

01:34:07.333 --> 01:34:08.708
Aku minta maaf, ya.

01:34:11.958 --> 01:34:12.958
Amira.

01:34:13.958 --> 01:34:15.083
Hari ini,

01:34:16.333 --> 01:34:17.833
